Package: readflex
Type: Package
Title: Flexible CSV Reader with Automatic Encoding Detection
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-06-21
Author: Toshihiro Iguchi <toshihiro.iguchi.github@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Toshihiro Iguchi <toshihiro.iguchi.github@gmail.com>
Description: Automatically detects character encodings and reads CSV files 
    with various text encodings commonly used worldwide. Supports UTF-8, 
    Shift_JIS, GB18030, Big5, EUC-KR, KOI8-R, Windows-1251, ISO-8859-1 
    and other encodings. Provides diagnostic tools, caching for performance,
    and handles multiple file formats including compressed files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
